Welcome to my portfolio blog! This is my first post using MDX and Contentlayer.

## Features

- **MDX Support**: Write JSX in markdown
- **TypeScript**: Full type safety
- **Contentlayer**: Automatic content processing

```javascript
console.log('Hello, World!')
```

This is just the beginning of my blogging journey!
